data.text:
GIMP is one of the most advanced pieces of free software available to professional and amateur artists and other image manipulation fields. Primarily the software serves a free alternative to Adobe Photoshop. The primary development team of the GNOME Foundation has been accepting Bitcoin donations for The GIMP.

See Also on BitcoinWiki
